    </Replace>
		<!--Storms-->
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_BLIZZARD_SIGNIFICANT_NAME">
			<Text>Significant Blizzard</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_BLIZZARD_SIGNIFICANT_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>An icy wind sweeps blanketing snow across the landscape, as living creatures huddle in their dens.</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_BLIZZARD_CRIPPLING_NAME">
			<Text>Crippling Blizzard</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_BLIZZARD_CRIPPLING_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>The howling wind and lashing snow turn sky and land white. Familiar forms disappear beneath frozen mounds.</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_DUST_STORM_GRADIENT_NAME">
			<Text>Gradient Dust Storm</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_DUST_STORM_GRADIENT_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>The sun is an angry orange disc in a hazy sky as people scurry about their business, cloth wrapped around noses and mouths.</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_DUST_STORM_HABOOB_NAME">
			<Text>Haboob Dust Storm</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_DUST_STORM_HABOOB_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>From far off people see the approaching wall of driven sand, and scatter to seek safety before the scouring wind!</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_TORNADO_FAMILY_NAME">
			<Text>Tornado Family</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_TORNADO_FAMILY_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>A tornado slowly descends from a summer storm, and people seek refuge.</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_TORNADO_OUTBREAK_NAME">
			<Text>Tornado Outbreak</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_TORNADO_OUTBREAK_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>A fast-moving line of storms gallop across the darkening summer sky, with tornadoes ominously forming beneath. </Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_HURRICANE_CAT_4_NAME">
			<Text>Category-4 Hurricane</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_HURRICANE_CAT_4_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Pelting rain and a howling gale mark the arrival of a mighty hurricane.</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_HURRICANE_CAT_5_NAME">
			<Text>Category-5 Hurricane</Text>
		</Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_HURRICANE_CAT_5_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>The wind screams, the torrents of rain fall, and the waves drive inexorably ashore. Little can stand where this hurricane passes!</Text>
		</Replace>
    <Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_DROUGHT_MAJOR_NAME">
      <Text>Major Drought</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_DROUGHT_MAJOR_DESCRIPTION">
      <Text>Locusts whirr and dust stirs in the hot wind. The land is parched by drought.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_DROUGHT_EXTREME_NAME">
      <Text>Withering Drought</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_RANDOM_EVENT_DROUGHT_EXTREME_DESCRIPTION">
      <Text>A merciless sun beats down on the drought-stricken and withered earth. No rain has fallen, and the skies promise no relief.</Text>
    </Replace>
